name: Alpha Pad
description: "A hybrid ecosystem comprising a LaunchPad and Incubation service brought to you by the team at Alpha Pad. Alpha Pad leverage our experience in the space and our network of experts bring to life the necessary components of every crypto project such as branding, website, socials, marketers, moderators and most importantly a strong community. APAD help bring your idea to life through connecting you with some of the best developers in the space to build out your product vision and help establish a roadmap for product delivery."
